                        <interp inst="t18510616-name-705" type="surname" value="CARTER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18510616-name-705" type="given" value="THOMAS WILLIAM"></interp>THOMAS WILLIAM CARTER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-inspector, L</hi>). I went after the prisoners, stopped them, and said I took them for stealing a handkerchief—Roffey said, "Here it is, I did not take it," taking it from his pocket, and giving it to me—this is it. (<hi rend="italic">Shade received a good character.</hi>)</p>
